IMPORTANT NOTICE REGARDING GAME ASSETS
=======================================

This repository contains NO copyrighted game assets or binary code from
Ratchet & Clank (PS2). The decompiled C source code in src/ was produced
solely through reverse engineering and is an original work created by
AG-RAC contributors.

Ratchet & Clank is a trademark of Sony Interactive Entertainment LLC.
Insomniac Games is a trademark of Insomniac Games, Inc.
This project is not affiliated with or endorsed by Sony Interactive
Entertainment or Insomniac Games.

To use the build system, you must provide your own legally obtained copy
of the game. The build system will extract necessary data from your copy
at build time. Distributing extracted game data is prohibited.
